form_values.2d29: Treated knotweed and areas of vegitaton that had not responded to the original vegetation spray. The overall effect of the last spray is still not known, majority of weed is dying off and where there where obvious gaps in treatment these have now been picked up. However it is important that another mop up inspection is done to ensure that the treatments are effective. There is further growths of weeds and regrowth on woody plants which will will need to be treated again later in the summer
